OL,3,CFamily feels 'shocked and unsafe'
OL,4,Cfollowing 'racial attack' on high
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FA woman from the Scottish Borders says
OL,8,Fshe feels unsafe and unwelcome after
OL,9,Fshe was racially abused in the street
OL,10,Fin front of her young daughter.
OL,12,FRazia Sultan says the abuse she
OL,13,Fexperienced whilst walking in Hawick
OL,14,Fhigh street with her 7-year-old and
OL,15,Fher mother has left her family fearing
OL,16,Ffor their safety.
OL,18,FThe alleged incident happened on
OL,19,FTuesday 16 September and was caught on
OL,20,Fcamera by Hawick TV's 'live cam' in
OL,21,Fthe town.
