OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Border Razia said:
OL,8,F"You can see me go back after I've
OL,9,Fheard him say 'you don't belong here'.
OL,10,FSo then I knew what this was. It was
OL,11,Fjust getting worse and then when he
OL,12,Fused the P word you knew it was racist.
OL,14,F"Because my mum visibly had her hijab
OL,15,Fon - and we do wear hijabs but that
OL,16,Fday me and my child were wearing
OL,17,Fbucket hats - you could tell it was
OL,18,Fbecause of that," she explained, "you
OL,19,Fcould visibly tell we were brown and
OL,20,Fyou could visibly tell we were muslim."
