OL,7,FRazia says it's the first time she's
OL,8,Fever experienced racism in the Borders
OL,9,F- and believes it's related to rising
OL,10,Ftensions and anti-immigration
OL,11,Fsentiment.
OL,13,F"We were born and brought up in
OL,14,FEngland," said Razia. "My mum's seen
OL,15,Fthe National Front and all these kind
OL,16,Fof things growing up but she's never
OL,17,Fhad a direct racial incident. I've
OL,18,Fnever had a direct racial incident.
OL,20,F"This is the first time and we were
OL,21,Fjust shocked," she added.
