OL,7,FShe says anti-immigration marches mean
OL,8,Fthat her family were already "on edge"
OL,9,Fbut during her ten years living in
OL,10,FScotland she has never experienced
OL,11,Fanything like this - and she's upset
OL,12,Fher daughter was there to witness it.
OL,14,FSpeaking about her child's reaction in
OL,15,Fthe moment, Razia said: "She was
OL,16,Fholding my hand so tight, she got
OL,17,Fscared, because the man he was a
OL,18,Fheavyset man, thinking he's going to
OL,19,Fcome towards us. I had to be brave for
OL,20,Fher."
