OL,7,F"It was just devastating because I had
OL,8,Fto explain to a 7-year-old that
OL,9,Fbecause of her religion and because of
OL,10,Fher skin colour - how do you explain
OL,11,Fthat this is why he's done it?"
OL,13,FAamer Anwar is a human rights lawyer
OL,14,Fand says immigration isn't a new thing
OL,15,Fbut incidents like the one reported by
OL,16,FRazia are on the rise.
