OL,7,FPolice Scotland told us: "Hate crime
OL,8,Fshould have no place in society and
OL,9,Fwill not be tolerated. Our officers
OL,10,Fare working tirelessly to tackle hate
OL,11,Fcrime following the implementation of
OL,12,Fthe Hate Crime and Public Order
OL,13,F(Scotland) Act.
OL,15,F"We want everyone targeted by hate
OL,16,Fcrime, or those who witness it, to
OL,17,Fhave confidence to come forward. They
OL,18,Fcan be assured they will be treated
OL,19,Fwith dignity and respect, and that the
OL,20,Fcircumstances they report will be
OL,21,Ffully investigated."
